Package org.ldaptive.io

Interface Summary
LdapResultReader Interface for reading ldap results.
LdapResultWriter Interface for writing ldap results.
ValueTranscoder<T> Interface for decoding and encoding custom types for ldap attribute values.
 

Class Summary
CertificateValueTranscoder Decodes and encodes a certificate for use in an ldap attribute value.
Dsmlv1Reader Reads DSML version 1 from a Reader and supplies an LdapResult.
Dsmlv1Writer Writes DSML version 1 to a Writer using an LdapResult.
LdifReader Reads an LDIF from a Reader and supplies an LdapResult.
LdifWriter Writes an LDIF to a Writer using an LdapResult.
